Deposit fee: 7 USDT + 9%.

How much do you charge for withdrawal?
Withdrawal fee: 7 USDT + 19%.

Are there any hidden fees?
No hidden fees. All commissions are transparent and fixed.

Do I pay a subscription fee?
No. There are no monthly or yearly subscriptions.

What payment methods are supported?
Deposits and withdrawals are in USDT (TRC-20).

Is there a gas fee to execute trades?
No. All trading execution costs are covered inside the system.

Раздел - Profit
Внутри раздела- How much profit can I expect daily?
On average, 1–9% daily profit. Results vary depending on market conditions.

What is the average monthly profit?
Historically, 40–150% monthly.

Are profits guaranteed?
No. Palladium does not guarantee profit. Both winning and losing trades exist, but historically profits outweigh losses.

Do you have losing trades too?
Yes. Transparency means we publish all trades, profitable and losing.

Is compounding possible?
Yes, profit is added to your balance and continues trading automatically.

Can I withdraw profit anytime?
Yes, withdrawals are available at any time.


Раздел - withdrawals
Внутри раздела -How long do withdrawals take?
From 10 minutes to 2–3 hours. Maximum up to 7 days in rare cases.

Is the withdrawal automatic or manual?
Automatic. The bot closes open trades and processes withdrawal.

Do I need to pass KYC for withdrawal?
No. Palladium does not require KYC for deposits or withdrawals.

What if withdrawal is delayed?
Contact support in Telegram. The system will still process your request.

Is there a withdrawal limit?
No fixed limit, but the bot must close active trades first.


Раздел - Safety 
Внитри раздела - Is my money safe with Palladium?
All operations are automated and transparent. Users control deposits and withdrawals.

Does Palladium have access to my exchange account?
No. The bot operates independently and does not require API keys.

Is Palladium regulated?
Palladium operates as a software service. There is no financial license.

Do you comply with AML / FATF rules?
Yes. Deposits are only accepted in crypto (USDT), no fiat or cash transfers.

What happens if the bot stops working?
The system is designed for high stability. If trading is paused, funds remain on your balance and are available for withdrawal.


